    • Method Detail

      • setCompareId

        void setCompareId​(boolean compareId)
        Marks that comparisons with this key requires also comparing entityId, this allows functionality of inclusive/exclusive bounds of range queries. This is because GBPTree only support from inclusive and to exclusive.

        Note that compareId is only an in memory state.

        abstract int compareValueTo​(SELF other)
